{"tid":793260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小朋友扯爛零食包裝餅乾散落一地 　　家長拒賠：細路仔唔好咁計較！","createTime":"2018-08-25T09:09:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T14:28:33.000Z","uid":202698,"like":1073,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":116,"replies":[{"pid":"e02b73461dbf8b419fdbfc62ac8347ed1a163ca6","tid":793260,"uid":202698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T09:09:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/25/170720_1257f74ab676156cb14ea9deeaf9fe4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F25%2F170720_1257f74ab676156cb14ea9deeaf9fe4a.jpg&h=3fb13790&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/799015-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E5%B0%8F%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B%E6%89%AF%E7%88%9B%E9%9B%B6%E9%A3%9F%E5%8C%85%E8%A3%9D%E9%A4%85%E4%B9%BE%E6%95%A3%E8%90%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%B0++%E5%AE%B6%E9%95%B7%E6%8B%92%E8%B3%A0%EF%BC%9A%E7%B4%B0%E8%B7%AF%E4%BB%94%E5%94%94%E5%A5%BD%E5%92%81%E8%A8%88%E8%BC%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F799015-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%259C%258B%25E5%258F%258B%25E6%2589%25AF%25E7%2588%259B%25E9%259B%25B6%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%258C%2585%25E8%25A3%259D%25E9%25A4%2585%25E4%25B9%25BE%25E6%2595%25A3%25E8%2590%25BD%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%259C%25B0%2B%2B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%258B%2592%25E8%25B3%25A0%25EF%25BC%259A%25E7%25B4%25B0%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E5%2592%2581%25E8%25A8%2588%25E8%25BC%2583&d=I7VlNXgm3wFYfUDknKxenr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=57e452eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F799015-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%259C%258B%25E5%258F%258B%25E6%2589%25AF%25E7%2588%259B%25E9%259B%25B6%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%258C%2585%25E8%25A3%259D%25E9%25A4%2585%25E4%25B9%25BE%25E6%2595%25A3%25E8%2590%25BD%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%259C%25B0%2B%2B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%258B%2592%25E8%25B3%25A0%25EF%25BC%259A%25E7%25B4%25B0%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E5%2592%2581%25E8%25A8%2588%25E8%25BC%2583&h=c4414467\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/799015-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E5%B0%8F%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B%E6%89%AF%E7%88%9B%E9%9B%B6%E9%A3%9F%E5%8C%85%E8%A3%9D%E9%A4%85%E4%B9%BE%E6%95%A3%E8%90%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%B0++%E5%AE%B6%E9%95%B7%E6%8B%92%E8%B3%A0%EF%BC%9A%E7%B4%B0%E8%B7%AF%E4%BB%94%E5%94%94%E5%A5%BD%E5%92%81%E8%A8%88%E8%BC%83</a><br />\n<br />\n不少小朋友見到新奇事物，總是手多多觸碰！有零食店店員就分享一次不愉快的經歷，<span style=\"color: red;\">指有小朋友在店內手多多將零食包裝扯爛，導致餅乾散落一地，惟其父母不但偷偷將餅乾掃至零食架下，被店員揭發更一度拒絕賠償，理直氣壯稱「小朋友手多啫，唔好咁計較」</span>。店員不禁在帖文中怒斥「幾時有細路仔做錯嘢唔使罰嘅錯覺？細路仔大晒？」。<br />\n<br />\n該名店員在社交網站facebook「西客之道 HIspitality」中抱怨，指有一家三口在店內購物時，<span style=\"color: red;\">小朋友「見到啲吊住嘅餅就係咁扯（唔知點解十個有九個細路都係咁）點知一扯，成條散晒，跌到成地都係餅</span>，呢對男女仲以為用掃落個架下邊就冇人知，咪以為阿姐我盲啦」。<br />\n<br />\n於是店員在該家人結帳時，要求對方賠償，怎料該名父親反駁稱<span style=\"color: red;\">「唔係囉，你邊到見到係我哋整爛呀，唔好乜都入我哋數啦」，而母親亦在一旁稱「小朋友手多啫，你唔好咁計較囉」、「小朋友啫你使唔使咁呀」</span>。店員氣極怒斥「小朋友又點先，一句小朋友唔通可以連舖拆埋？唔想畀錢就睇住小朋友唔該！」。<br />\n<br />\n最終該對父母在店員堅持下，作出賠償，臨離開前更不忘拿走散開的餅乾「屍骸」，並聲稱「畀咗錢嘅，幾大都要攞埋呀！」。該行為引起店員不滿，在帖文中怒斥「細路仔大晒？」<br />\n<br />\n事件引起不少網民共嗚，有人留言讚店主做得好、「最x憎人地講細路仔，知道個仔冇人性，唔該睇實啲。唔怪細路無人性，只怪老豆老母唔盡責」、「好多老豆老母都係唔會睇住啲細路，諗住個員工同佢睇埋」。"},{"pid":"54dd4b155cc70a0db885adbc5f3a552ab7e541a8","tid":793260,"uid":151664,"like":908,"dislike":2,"score":906,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T09:11:01.000Z","msg":"垃圾家長，唔識教個細路，學咩人生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0b41aa45e9674032353337089064bb08ebb31e","tid":793260,"uid":85751,"like":227,"dislike":4,"score":223,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T09:11:22.000Z","msg":"打鳩個細路"},{"pid":"3cb2c7fe15e36f1784594b6c3cf4168be09ce51c","tid":793260,"uid":200328,"like":572,"dislike":3,"score":569,"citedBy":2,"replyTime